Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke's Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.99,0:00:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not another copy of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're quite a guy to be able to do\Na Partial Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at controlling\Nyour Curse Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.27,0:00:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strong! Haven't seen a copycat\Nthis good since Kimimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.77,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish to talk to you, Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?! Without him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Without him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...guys... How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value your life,\Ndon't go beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon lives there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's known as "Bipolar Jugo."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of Jugo,\Nno one lives in that village, to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's ever gotten close to him\Nand come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to lecture you.\NBut you should go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You've followed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But stop where you are.\NYou must not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go back to your own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come near me! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come here, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill anyone who comes in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away! I said to go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kimimaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:28.74,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(825.938,595)}Formation! \N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it once more.\NI have no intention of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kill that guy...Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'll let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mean!\NYou tricked me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You went and got lost on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just followed your directions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you accusing me of tricking you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I benefit from\Ntricking you anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be alone with Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A-As if I'd want such a thing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.\NBut what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo went wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the two of you went to Jugo,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He went out with Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's Sasuke.\NHe won't get beaten that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So Jugo is strong strong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you said that he willingly\Ncame to Orochimaru, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To reform himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.92,0:08:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Reform himself...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible that...for Jugo,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru's hideout was like\Na sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Jugo wish to be\Nreformed from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an addiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't do anything about it\Non his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to suppress his urge to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can no longer escape from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Your strength is amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro... I came in search of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you...\Nlike to go to Lord Orochimaru too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many people with Lord Orochimaru\N that are just like you and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all alone, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.11,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you go to Lord Orochimaru,\Nyou won't be alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not normal.\NI can't control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling when I'll start killing\Nthe people around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you...afraid of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not, Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.05,0:10:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become your cage...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm by your side...\Nyour spirit will be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll beat you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that...true?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm going to absorb the enzyme\Nfrom your body into my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you,\NI will possess the power of the Curse Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Curse Mark doesn't adapt\Nto just anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't adapt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I know... At that moment, I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know, then stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's part of the treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is being eaten away\Nby disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps your Curse Mark\Nwill slow its progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power will save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. We're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no way your power\Nwill reject me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kimimaro...why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did you...leave me and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're using a different technique\Nthan before, Jugo. It's solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Suigetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Suigetsu. I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is dangerous,\Nafter all, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't come here to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that anything\Nyou say will get through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to take him by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep going! Just kill each other off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you both...want me to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just now...that was real bloodthirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-You're irresistible...Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hurry up and lock me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo... I only came to free you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to kill anymore people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go outside...\NLeave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?\NTalk about split personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you so...\NJugo has this uncontrollable urge to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's unable to suppress the urge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,even though he really doesn't want\Nto kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when\NI'll kill someone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So just put the lock on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this guy is dangerous, Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even walk in front of him\Nwithout getting nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you guys?!\NJust leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And this hideout has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stay here, you'll die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine with me...\NI don't want to kill anyone ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry...\NI will become your cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who can make\Nthese urges stop is Kimimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Kimimaro, I won't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro? You mean\Nof the Kaguya clan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Jugo and Kimimaro were\Nespecially favored by Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They were kept together in this hideout\Nfor human experiments for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, Kimimaro was strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo was valuable for\Nhuman experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and Kimimaro was the only one able to\Nstop Jugo's rampages without hurting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought that guy was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo... Kimimaro died for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Died for your sake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke Uchiha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being sent out?\NYou're sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This has never happened before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who is taking my place\Nas Lord Orochimaru's vessel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he worth going that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.07,0:16:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take me out of the running\Nas a vessel, then there is no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He is like my reincarnation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will risk my life to bring him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you, Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power made me much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well Jugo... I'll be back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that how it is...Kimimaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have all the members I had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will tell you my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My goal is to kill Itachi Uchiha\Nof the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itachi Uchiha...?\N{\i1}But that's his brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to borrow your strength for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin... You said you had business\Nto take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well... On second thought,\Nit's not that urgent...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin... Be honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't being with Sasuke\Nall you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true!\NWhoever said such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...! I...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,See, I hit it right on the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're speechless.\NSo obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago...\Nyou had a crush on Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu, don't get Karin so worked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to be cooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... Sorry, Karin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But as much as you hate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sticking to Sasuke like glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At least until I possess one\Nof the Seven Hidden Mist Blades...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisame Hoshigaki's\NGreat Shark Fin sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're just sword collecting?\NHow lame...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Jugo, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kimimaro used to say that\Nyou were his reincarnation, Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And he bet his life to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to see with my own eyes\N just how great of a Ninja you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru is dead,\Nso why isn't he returning to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke is possessed by\Nthe desire for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He intends to approach the Akatsuki\N in order to kill his older brother Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy!\NIs he still...? Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From this point on, we move together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And henceforth,\Nwe will call ourselves... Hebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation "Track Akatsuki"\Nis still ongoing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hunt down the Akatsuki first we'll\N definitely run into Sasuke eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:19:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hebi has but one objective...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, our target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi...
